From: Kishon Vijay Abraham I <kishon@ti.com>
Date: Fri, 18 Oct 2013 15:29:30 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 0651/1115] ARM: OMAP: Enable PCI for DRA7

Now that we have added PCIe driver for DRA7 SOCs, enable PCI on
DRA7 SOCs.

Signed-off-by: Kishon Vijay Abraham I <kishon@ti.com>
(cherry picked from commit 7b14a66d766bd7909d05e9ca84eeaf99df01cc89)
Signed-off-by: Zumeng Chen <zumeng.chen@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm/mach-omap2/Kconfig |    1 +
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/mach-omap2/Kconfig b/arch/arm/mach-omap2/Kconfig
index 8234aa3..1d119bd 100644
--- a/arch/arm/mach-omap2/Kconfig
+++ b/arch/arm/mach-omap2/Kconfig
@@ -129,6 +129,7 @@ config SOC_DRA7XX
 	select CROSSBAR
 	select ARCH_HAS_RESET_CONTROLLER
 	select RESET_TI
+	select PCI
 
 comment "OMAP Core Type"
 	depends on ARCH_OMAP2
